	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />Source code for the menu doesn't really matter.  The custom mapper you'd need for a particular multicart is what matters.
<br />
<br />If you want to modify an existing multicart to replace games of the exact same size, you could do it without source code.

		

		</td>
